# Google Sign-In — paste the **Web client (auto created by Google Service)** Client ID
# from Firebase Console → Project settings → Your apps (or Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials).
# This MUST be the Web Client ID, NOT the Android/iOS one — see CLAUDE.md for setup.
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID=